<tal:macro metal:use-macro="view.site_style">
    <tal:content metal:fill-slot="content">
        
        <h1>Download Ticket: ${ticket.__name__}</h1><br />
        <div style="background-color:white;border:1px solid #666;width:206px;" class="pull-left" tal:condition="view.photo_required">
            <img src="${request.route_path('guest_profile_photo', tick_id=ticket.__name__)}" width="200" style="margin:3px;" />
        </div>
        
        Tickets can be downloaded in a number of ways to make entering the event as easy as possible for you. The first option is to print-off a ticket, by choosing this option you will be presented with a PDF that you will need to print and bring with you on the day of the event. The second option is to download a Passbook ticket for your iOS device, this will add itself to the Passbook app on your phone and can just be presented at entry on the day.<br /><br />
        
        <table class="table table-striped table-bordered">
            <thead>
                <th class="span9">Ticket Download Method</th>
                <th>Actions</th>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <h4 style="margin:0 0 5px 0;padding:0;">Print Your Ticket</h4>
                        <span style="color:#666">Download and print-out a copy of your ticket to present at the entrance to the event.</span>
                    </td>
                    <td style="line-height:80px;vertical-align:middle;">
                        <a href="${request.route_path('ticket_download_method', tick_id=ticket.__name__, method='pdf')}" class="ll_btn pull-left" id="pay-stripe">
                            <i class="icon-print"></i><span class="pull-right">Print Ticket</span>
                        </a>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <h4 style="margin:0 0 5px 0;padding:0;">Download a Passbook Ticket</h4>
                        <span style="color:#666">Download an electronic ticket to use in Passbook on your iPhone, simply present the ticket on your phone when entering the event.</span>
                    </td>
                    <td style="line-height:80px;vertical-align:middle;">
                        <a href="${request.route_path('ticket_download_method', tick_id=ticket.__name__, method='passbook')}" class="ll_btn pull-left" id="pay-stripe">
                            <i class="icon-arrow-down"></i><span class="pull-right">Get Passbook Ticket</span>
                        </a>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                    
            </tbody>
        </table>
        

		<div class="clearline"></div>

		<a href="${request.route_path('user_profile')}" class="ll_btn pull-left">
			<i class="icon-arrow-left pull-left"></i>
			<span class="pull-right">Back</span>
		</a>
		<div class="clearline"></div>
		<br /><br />
        
    </tal:content>
</tal:macro>